<h3 class="date"><a href="/2008/mar/03/">&#x27a0;</a> March 3, 2008</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="nine-inch-nails-ghosts" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://ghosts.nin.com/">Nine Inch Nails - Ghosts</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>Trent Reznor releases a new NIN album as online download with &#8220;premium&#8221; collectors offerings.  Notable differences to the Radiohead &#8220;In Rainbows&#8217; download include a) It&#8217;s CC BY-NC-SA licensed, so you can remix it however you like and b) The first part has been &#8220;officially&#8221; seeded to BitTorrent in a shareware stylee.</p>

