        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.slate.com/id/2177432/">Rock Band vs. Real Band: Sleater-Kinney&#39;s guitarist tests out Rock Band. - By Carrie Brownstein - Slate Magazine</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>Greate article on &#8220;Rock Band&#8221; by Carrie Brownstein.  &#8220;If you are going to play the game with a group of friends for more than a night, shouldn&#8217;t you just form a real band? There is something sad about the thought of four teenagers getting Rock Band for Christmas and spending all of their after-school time pretending to know how to play.&#8221;</p>

