        <a href="http://flickr.com/photos/groovymother/2067508509/"><img class="flickrphoto" alt="Audible Awesomeness" src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2252/2067508509_c4472b293d_m.jpg" height="180" width="240" /></a>

